data.description: Stunning 3-Bedroom Cape Retreat with Pool and Modern Comfort.  Discover this charming 3-bed, 2-bath Cape retreat in a highly sought-after location, close to restaurants, entertainment, and stunning views. An open floor plan seamlessly connects indoor and outdoor spaces for relaxation and entertaining. The functional kitchen is getting a fresh update with brand-new stainless steel appliances, including a fridge, stove, microwave, and dishwasher.  Step into your private oasis with a screened and heated pool, surrounded by a new black chain-link fence. Recent upgrades, such as a new roof, gutters, fascia, water heater, exterior AND exterior paint, ensure peace of mind.  In addition to three bedrooms, this property offers a versatile flex room, perfect for a den, formal dining room, office, or a potential 4th bedroom. This well-maintained property is ready for you to make it your own and embrace the Cape lifestyle. BUT Wait There's MORE SELLER WILL PAY 10,000.00, TOWARDS BUYER'S CLOSING COSTS, PREPAIDS, OR KITCHEN UPGRADES.!!!  Don't miss this opportunity—schedule a showing today!
